general.desc: PT Kobexindo Tractors Tbk together with its subsidiaries is engaged in the distribution and service of heavy equipment and industrial machinery in Indonesia. The company offers excavators, articulated dump trucks, wheel loaders, hydraulic crawlers, and forklifts. The company's segment comprises of Heavy Equipment, Spare parts sales, Repair services and Mining Contractor services, Heavy Equipment Rentals, and Building Rental segments.
general.short_desc: PT Kobexindo Tractors Tbk distributes and services heavy equipment and industrial machineries in Indonesia. The Company offers heavy duty trucks, dump trucks, and among others.
